
  THE BASICS

kernel is the bunch of codes that interact with the hardware.
Kernel functions at a basic level, maintaining resources like RAM and CPU, communicating with hardware.

When you visit a website eg:google.com kernel code runs for 
Typing in the address
handling every network packet
writing history files to disk 
allocating memory 
communicating with graphics card 

How to call kenerl code :
System Calls 
Open a file (open)
start a program (execve)

STRACE:

strace -etrace= open google-chrome

FTRACE:
/proc
